internal_tempf.name: internal_tempf
internal_tempf.description: The internal temperature reading in Fahrenheit. Because the SNMP Protocol does not support floating point numbers, values are scaled by 100 and should be divided by 100 to get the actual value.

internal_tempc.name: internal_tempc

internal_humidity.name: internal_humidity

internal_heat_index.name: internal_heat_index
